  patient_id STRING OPTIONS(description='The \"patient_id\" field uniquely identifies the patient associated with the encounter. It is a critical element for linking encounters to patient records, ensuring accurate patient tracking, and maintaining continuity of care. This identifier is typically unique within a healthcare system, facilitating interoperability and data exchange.'),
